Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.53,0:02:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下子我们两个人\N可以独占猎物了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.85,0:02:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第五十三话\N巨人对抗超人\N射入绝望深渊的一只箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怪物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.76,0:02:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…我们完蛋了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.04,0:02:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 人最重要的\N是要懂得死心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.21,0:02:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该要勇敢地迎接死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.45,0:02:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 大家伤痕累累\N好不容易撑到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在苍紫大人终于要\N回来的这时刻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.85,0:02:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然在最后一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.42,0:03:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑出这样子的怪物来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.33,0:03:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.26,0:03:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.49,0:03:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想死心 我跟剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好要大家一起回东京的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…这次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.83,0:03:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许真的不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.94,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.48,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切还没有结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.89,0:03:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很快的…剑心就会回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会打倒志志雄他们\N回来这里呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.03,0:03:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前我们绝不能放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦  祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.10,0:03:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.43,0:03:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算妖怪出现  世界末日到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要信守与剑心的约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.87,0:03:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是…看来他完全不了解\N自己的处境呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.31,0:03:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来好好教导你们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.81,0:04:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是一线希望也没有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.65,0:04:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于理论观点\N所做的情况说明 第一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先看绯村拔刀斋回来的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.49,0:04:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以结论来说\N那可能性几乎等于零
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.07,0:04:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄大人认真起来\N可是必杀必胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.54,0:04:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拔刀斋的死亡比火焰还要明显
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.04,0:04:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死人要回去的地方\N不是这里 是阴曹地府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.11,0:04:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于理论观点\N所做的情况说明 第二点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.62,0:04:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的战力分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.59,0:04:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N以你们女人小孩的组合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能击败十本刀中的三人\N算是相当了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.86,0:04:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那激烈战斗的结果\N使你们伤痕累累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲白点 一点战力也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.47,0:04:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于理论观点\N所做的情况说明 第三点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们破军的战力分析
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.61,0:05:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必我说 用看的最快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.96,0:05:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翁大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.73,0:05:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基于以上一二三条\N得出一个结论
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.50,0:05:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们是完全没有希望\N只有死路一条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.07,0:05:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.98,0:05:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.21,0:05:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,理由不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.21,0:05:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人说什么我都相信剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信拔刀斋会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.89,0:05:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死前把梦与现实混为一谈啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.19,0:05:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比你多活好几倍岁数的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会好好教导你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.06,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信人就会被人背叛\N这是世间的道理啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.17,0:05:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.11,0:06:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.11,0:06:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心  祢彦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.21,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿薰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.47,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好 小鬼 说得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.27,0:07:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场仗是你这到最后\N仍相信我的傻徒弟的人获胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.78,0:07:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流现任继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.15,0:07:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村的师父 比古清十郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.02,0:07:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.55,0:07:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.42,0:07:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心说他有预先做好准备\N原来是指比古师父啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.08,0:07:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他接下那个怪物的刀\N还把刀弹开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.45,0:08:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 小鬼 人一放心\N就连腰也挺不起来啦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少喽嗦 你要来怎么不早来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要装酷也该有个限度的 这混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.23,0:08:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有意见去找我的傻徒弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.74,0:08:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他没告诉我这儿正确位置\N全都是他的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.44,0:08:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是找遍了全京都呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.28,0:08:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险 你退后点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.95,0:08:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.22,0:08:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…应该开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.52,0:08:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 很久没看到\N这么有神的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.79,0:08:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一刀相当不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.83,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生冲突时…手握得更紧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很遵守武术的基础嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是斩人拔刀斋的师父吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.71,0:08:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然能接下不二的大刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.14,0:08:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜不管你这只蚂蚁再厉害\N也经不起巨象一击的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能敌得过\N不二这个世纪怪物的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老头子要自言自语请到旁边说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.62,0:09:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.72,0:09:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在跟破军不二\N这个男人讲话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讲话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.10,0:09:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟怪物讲话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.80,0:09:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种怪物听得懂人话吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.00,0:09:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我接下他的一刀\N这就已经足够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.74,0:09:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一刀已经道出了他自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.68,0:09:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并非如那老头所想的\N光是身体巨大而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.35,0:09:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你决不是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.48,0:09:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你才是这时代\N罕见的真正的武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.92,0:09:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去从没有人理解真正的你\N因为你的怪异长相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.93,0:09:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你受到人们误解\N吃过不少苦头吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.47,0:09:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不二 应该结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.84,0:09:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再受头脑比你更笨的主人利用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.18,0:10:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头脑更笨？你说我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.94,0:10:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是武士呀  找回你的尊严吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.82,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别听他胡说 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要听我的话就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.59,0:10:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是没有我 你早死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.56,0:10:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘记我的大恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.33,0:10:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因我你才能活着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.56,0:10:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二 你要听话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.84,0:10:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了  在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.51,0:10:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然逃到这里  终于追到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他来了 别害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.05,0:10:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这里 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.75,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是人 是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.29,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 他是妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.05,0:10:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放着不管一定会把大家吃掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请快打死他呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.99,0:10:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.90,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时你满身是血倒在地上\N是我救了你的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.64,0:11:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要想着报恩就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.45,0:11:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在跟不二讲话 你住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.35,0:11:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕  不愧是师父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二 拿下铠甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.32,0:11:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身心都穿着那么重的铠甲\N你是敌不过我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.26,0:11:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.73,0:11:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他想说自己最厉害\N这个人太自大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.07,0:11:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢  好酷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.44,0:11:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.97,0:11:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别被他迷惑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是扰乱你 骗你脱下铠甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.71,0:11:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,减低你的防御力的诡计啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.08,0:11:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经象个武士\N为你的傻主人尽忠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.65,0:11:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,某人实在应该向你看齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.25,0:11:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过 你差不多到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.76,0:11:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以自我意志选择战斗的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.63,0:12:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你全力以赴都打不倒的男人\N头一次站在你面前哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是欢喜的泪水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢喜的泪水？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.45,0:13:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能他这一生没有任何一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.52,0:13:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他视为一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.09,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都把他看作是怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是比古大人看出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的悲伤与他的武士魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.80,0:13:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不二被打动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎 多了不起的男人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卸下铠甲以后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.08,0:13:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他好象变得更强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很不妙吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 这样最好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.92,0:13:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这哪里好了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心\N但他都那么潇洒的说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.09,0:13:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太酷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.03,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.10,0:13:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.24,0:13:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来光明正大的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.84,0:14:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在取距离吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.87,0:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二停下来的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好在比古的攻击距离的\N一步之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.18,0:14:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种高手所取的间距\N可以说是剑的结界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二无法再往前进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.78,0:14:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个胶着状态\N暂时还会持续下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.75,0:14:41.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 胜负就在一瞬之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.86,0:14:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二使出浑身力量的一刀\N就看比古大人如何接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但愿如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.70,0:14:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这场决斗\N无法在瞬间分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.04,0:14:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一带恐怕会化成废墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.57,0:15:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都喽嗦死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.44,0:15:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎是剑心的师父耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必我们在那儿担心\N他早就看清一切了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 一定会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 身体僵硬在那里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.02,0:15:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是这么的害怕我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.03,0:15:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两手握刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.74,0:15:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.44,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来还有这招\N这样的话威力就加倍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.07,0:16:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尸骨无存呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.24,0:16:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是不二厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们破军最强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.31,0:16:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说是吧 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那一击…真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 太可惜了 不二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.71,0:16:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞天御剑流 九头龙闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.30,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有手下留情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.84,0:17:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他与剑心决定性的不同点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.81,0:17:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.38,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刀刃向上就象逆刃刀一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.51,0:17:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.92,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身体大 生命力也强劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度的攻击\N还不致于让他死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太酷了 比古大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后那一刀太了不起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.20,0:17:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不二头一次能够跟\N理解自己的人全力战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.04,0:17:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以剑来交流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.60,0:17:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算被打败 也可以满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.28,0:17:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这边这个好象也没有死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.14,0:17:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来他是只会说大话的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.51,0:17:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界就是这样\N往往这种人活最长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.78,0:17:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同样身为老人  我真以他为耻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.76,0:18:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是 虽然不晓得\N他是否能活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之这样算是完成\N傻徒弟拜托的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的就是相信他  等待他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.58,0:18:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们…赢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.46,0:18:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们守住与剑心的约定了 万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.83,0:18:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只要等剑心回来就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.63,0:18:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.10,0:18:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 刚刚听到阿薰的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.24,0:18:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很正常啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.28,0:19:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为伤口\N使你头壳发烧了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.92,0:19:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太没礼貌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.25,0:19:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然可能是错觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能听到阿薰的声音\N我就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋一定是平安无事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人太过乐观了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.73,0:19:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的那么相信吗\N你拜托的那个师父…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.36,0:19:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比古清十郎那个人\N从来没有背信过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.87,0:19:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美丽的师徒关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.98,0:19:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 方治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.11,0:19:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,京都的通讯兵打来电报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,葵屋袭击行动失败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.92,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夷腕坊逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.69,0:19:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蝙也、镰足、不二、才槌\N成了敌人俘虏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.92,0:19:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说\N十本刀几乎等于全灭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.80,0:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我连不二都派去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.17,0:19:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个阵容应该不会失败的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.83,0:19:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.93,0:19:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对方比我们强 只是如此而已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.24,0:20:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世间是弱肉强食
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.85,0:20:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.38,0:20:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我很强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.22,0:20:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只要以我的能力\N祢补十本刀的其他人就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.76,0:20:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 我去去就回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他又让我吃惊了一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面对这个状况\N他一点也没有受到动摇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.47,0:20:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他失去愤怒与悲伤的感觉很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.68,0:20:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是他的行动理念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.78,0:20:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强者活下去 弱者死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.09,0:20:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我教导他的话\N也是世间唯一的真实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.19,0:20:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 你太过份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 你生气什么\N亏我还带着你跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.67,0:21:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,象只狗一样被拧着跑\N哪个女人会高兴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.20,0:21:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这样可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.47,0:21:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.64,0:21:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美 那是下一个房间吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.82,0:21:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了\N你们应该知道是谁在等吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.89,0:21:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天剑宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.42,0:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过好几次他的名字\N他很强吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.49,0:21:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是十本刀最强的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.90,0:21:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前把我的逆刃刀\N分成两半的青年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢相信 在拔刀术上\N还有人能够超越剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.87,0:21:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候算是平手吧\N双方都撤退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.21,0:21:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果继续下去 谁会赢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.08,0:21:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看双方的剑就晓得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.12,0:21:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是现在的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.79,0:21:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学会逆刃刀的真髓\N与绝招天翔龙闪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.03,0:22:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且最主要的是\N这是场绝不能输的仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.37,0:22:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.73,0:22:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入这扇门\N你就再也无法回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.04,0:22:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于天剑宗次郎没有感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.27,0:22:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以敌人无法洞察到\N他那天衣无缝的身法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.68,0:22:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且他有另一个素质\N是当时拔刀斋没看到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.18,0:22:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是使他成功\N暗杀大久保卿的真正才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.86,0:22:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我亲自找到\N塑造出来的最强的修罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.16,0:22:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,濑田宗次郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.16,0:22:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底能不能打倒他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.90,0:22:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让我看看你的能耐吧 拔刀斋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.54,0:22:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临 绯村
